summary: Saved game of a beautiful lvl 1 Woodelf.
descriptionHtml:
-A beautiful innocent Woodelf can be decieving. Depending on what you decide. ^_^-

(Saved right after Helgen, alongside the river near Riverwood.)

(No cheats are active.)

(If you want the character to look exactly like the one in the pictures, then you should download these wonderful mods.)
